videos.headline: Texas hooks an easy TD early in 1st
videos.description: Shane Buechele fakes a handoff and finds Daniel Young wide open for a Longhorn touchdown.

videos.headline: Young runs loose putting Longhorns in red zone
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger connects with Daniel Young for 42 yards putting Texas in red zone.

videos.headline: Texas' Burt scores his first TD of the season
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger finds John Burt the pylon with great foot placement, giving the Longhorns a second touchdown.

videos.headline: Tigers' Witter pounces his way into end zone
videos.description: Ish Witter receives the handoff and runs into the end zone for Missouri's first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Wheeler's scoop and score stampedes into end zone for Texas
videos.description: Missouri's Ish Witter fumbles the ball and Texas' Anthony Wheeler takes it the house for a 38-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Tigers' keep stepping on their own tail
videos.description: Missouri's Albert Okwuegbunam fumbles the ball and is recovered by Texas' Breckyn Hager.

videos.headline: Herman: 'I haven't seen a call like that in 20 years of coaching'
videos.description: Tom Herman is confused on the personal foul called on RB Daniel Young, and discusses Texas' defense.

videos.headline: Longhorns' Young butts heads with Tigers' Frazier
videos.description: Texas' Daniel Young gets a personal foul penalty after he gets tackled by Missouri's Marcell Frazier and a sideline scuffle ensues.

videos.headline: Tigers strike back with TD on first play of second half
videos.description: Drew Lock launches the ball to Johnathon Johnson, who beats the coverage with his long strides for a 79-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Bad snap results in Texas safety
videos.description: Missouri's Trystan Castillo snaps the ball over Drew Lock's head that results in safety.

videos.headline: Longhorns' capture interception
videos.description: Drew Lock's pass is intercepted by Texas' Davante Davis.

videos.headline: Longhorns' Foreman charges into end zone on reverse play
videos.description: Armanti Foreman gets pitched the ball on an reverse play and runs the ball in for a Texas touchdown.

videos.headline: Texas' Wheeler ejected from game for targeting
videos.description: Anthony Wheeler leaves game in the last minute of the game on a targeting call.

videos.headline: Longhorns' Dickson finishes strong in last game
videos.description: Longhorns' Michael Dickson had 10 of 11 punts inside the Missouri 20-yard line, and shares what it means to finish his college career with a bowl game win.

videos.headline: Texas defeats Missouri in the Texas Bowl 33-16
videos.description: ESPN's Dusty Dvoracek and Adam Amin analyze the balanced first half of Wednesday night's Texas Bowl, and the Longhorns' impressive performance.

videos.headline: Coach Herman presented with bowl game trophy
videos.description: Coach Tom Herman shares what it means to win the Academy Sports and Outdoors Texas Bowl, and how his punter is the MVP and player of the game.

videos.headline: Texas finishes season with a W
videos.description: Texas' defense forces four turnovers and the Longhorns get an Armanti Foreman touchdown late to seal a 33-16 win against Missouri.
